Honolulu.Dole Middle School: Governor Sanford Ballard Dole Middle School, known better as Dole Middle School, is a public middle school located in Kalihi Valley on the island of Oahu in Honolulu, Hawaii. Its former name was Kalihi Middle School, and it was named after Sanford Ballard Dole in 1956. Dole Middle School provides education for students in grades 6, 7 and 8.
